import { Fragment } from 'react'
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Routes,
  Route
} from 'react-router-dom'
import './App.css'

// import components
import Navigation from './components/Layout/Navigation'
import Home from './components/Layout/Home'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Fragment>
        <Navigation />
        <Routes>
          <Route exact path='/' component={Home} />
        </Routes>
      </Fragment>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
